Titolo: Sally Face

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Sally Face is an indie adventure game created by Steve Gabry, aka Portable Moose. The game follows the titular main character Sal Fisher (otherwise known as Sally Face), a boy with a prosthetic face, who investigates local murders with his friends. The game consists of 5 episodes that were released between 2016â€“2019. Sally Face also released on Nintendo Switch in 2021.